  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/764430/extras/0ba64446bfd27ead3ef83573dd6387d3.avif?t=1728368044\" width=616 height=352 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Storyline:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Cadiaden Empire and the Titeserret Kingdom were at war.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A mercenaries, Kaim! He is going to The Cadiaden Empire with His companion. On the way, they met a girl. She is the princess of the Titeserret Kingdom. So they took the job of escort her back to Titeserret.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team is composed of 3 characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 30 different monsters to fight, each with their own strengths, and modifiers for them as well for even more variety.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >High-quality maps, monsters and graphics, along with a lush music score enhance the experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exciting story full of twists and witty or hilarious dialogs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lovable, addicting characters</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/764430/extras/0ba64446bfd27ead3ef83573dd6387d3.avif?t=1728368044\" width=616 height=352 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Storyline:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Cadiaden Empire and the Titeserret Kingdom were at war.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A mercenaries, Kaim! He is going to The Cadiaden Empire with His companion. On the way, they met a girl. She is the princess of the Titeserret Kingdom. So they took the job of escort her back to Titeserret.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team is composed of 3 characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 30 different monsters to fight, each with their own strengths, and modifiers for them as well for even more variety.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >High-quality maps, monsters and graphics, along with a lush music score enhance the experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exciting story full of twists and witty or hilarious dialogs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lovable, addicting characters</p></li></ul>",
